items.name: dd-core
items.description: Rust-based VST plugin development library with hardware accelerated GUI support.

items.name: PineappleSynth
items.description: A too simple vsti synth made with wdl-ol

items.name: midiAuralizer
items.description: GUI to render MIDI Files through VST Instruments with an extended Protocol.

items.name: azr3-mac
items.description: Mac OS X port of Rumpelrausch's drawbar organ VST instrument plugin.

items.name: msm5232wsg
items.description: This script creates wavetables that I tried to imitate OKI MSM5232 tones. A .fxb file for Chip32 VSTi and 15 wave files will be created and wave files are readable for SONICWARE ELZ_1 synthesizer.

items.name: kamata2wav
items.description: This script converts a kamata user file with extension .kamata_programs, which is made by KORG gadget 2 VSTi, into WAV files for SONICWARE ELZ_1 synthesizer.

items.name: msm5232wavs
items.description: This script creates 15 wavetables that I tried to imitate OKI MSM5232 tones. Wave files are readable for SONICWARE ELZ_1 synthesizer.

items.name: msm5232kamata
items.description: This script creates 15 wavetables that I tried to imitate OKI MSM5232 sound chip tones and makes a .kamata_programs file for the Korg Gadget 2 kamata VSTi.

items.name: chip32fxb2wav
items.description: This script converts a user file with extension .fxb, which is made by Chip32(Sam) VSTi, into WAV files for SONICWARE ELZ_1 synthesizer.
